posting_body: ['PROPERTY INFO', 'ID: 14276098', 'Rent: $2,775 / Month', 'Beds: 1', 'Bath: 1', 'Available Date: 10/01/2022', 'Pet: Pet Friendly', 'Rent Includes:: Heat, Hot Water', 'Amazing Commonwealth Avenue location.', ' Beautiful brownstone around the corner from Copley Square, Newbury Street and the Prudential Center.', ' Unit is totally renovated with stylish island, dishwasher, high ceilings, original detail.', ' Includes heat and hot water, laundry in building.', ' Pet friendly.', 'Totally renovated brownstone on sunny side of Commonwealth Avenue in the grid of the Back Bay.', 'Close to Newbury Street, Prudential, Copley, Boston Commons, Beacon Hill, South End, financial district Harvard, MIT, Charles River and everything Boston has to offer.', ' Several one beds available starting at different dates throughout the summer.', 'Pets considered, both dogs and cats.', 'Elevator and laundry in building', 'WE ACCEPT VISA MASTERCARD & AMERICAN EXPRESS']
